1
00:00:00,020 --> 00:00:05,080
♪ Inside the state a city is built ♪

2
00:00:05,080 --> 00:00:10,190
♪ Where a benevolent emperor resides ♪

3
00:00:10,190 --> 00:00:15,330
♪ Court officials are brave and able ♪

4
00:00:15,330 --> 00:00:22,750
♪ The empress is fair ♪

5
00:00:25,580 --> 00:00:30,710
♪ Princes died too young to ascend the throne ♪

6
00:00:30,710 --> 00:00:35,570
♪ Princesses are spoiled and fragile ♪

7
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:40,270
♪ Commoners are also the emperor’s children ♪

8
00:00:40,830 --> 00:00:49,630
♪ All are living peacefully ♪

9
00:00:49,930 --> 00:00:54,280
♪ Wish I could live a day for myself ♪

10
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:59,380
♪ Follow my heart and ethics without distractions ♪

11
00:01:00,710 --> 00:01:03,400
♪ To be a good husband ♪

12
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:05,970
♪ To be a caring father ♪

13
00:01:06,460 --> 00:01:10,110
♪ We were close when we first met ♪

14
00:01:10,460 --> 00:01:14,710
♪ I hope I can control my desires ♪

15
00:01:15,540 --> 00:01:20,060
♪ To be a worriless emperor and father ♪

16
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:23,860
♪ Prudence tops all virtues ♪

17
00:01:23,860 --> 00:01:26,480
♪ People build the state ♪

18
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:30,020
= Held in the Lonely Castle =
♪ May the world be peaceful ♪

19
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:32,980
= Episode 4 =

20
00:01:38,180 --> 00:01:39,620
Your Majesty, Prime Minister Wang is here.

21
00:01:40,340 --> 00:01:44,300
= Emperor Zhao Zhen =

22
00:01:48,100 --> 00:01:48,740
Your Majesty,

23
00:01:49,060 --> 00:01:51,420
today we’re going to learn the
strategies of Gao Yao.

24
00:01:56,180 --> 00:01:57,060
What do you think of Cheng Lin,

25
00:01:57,460 --> 00:01:58,820
Prime Minister?

26
00:02:03,180 --> 00:02:05,660
= Wang Zeng, courtesy name Xiaoxian =
Cheng Lin has been an official for 10 years.

27
00:02:06,620 --> 00:02:08,340
He is diligent and upright,

28
00:02:08,660 --> 00:02:09,540
talented at management.

29
00:02:10,380 --> 00:02:11,300
Upright?

30
00:02:12,700 --> 00:02:14,180
Then how do you see

31
00:02:14,420 --> 00:02:16,420
his offering the painting of Empress
Dowager Wu attending state affairs?

32
00:02:17,420 --> 00:02:18,460
The late Emperor just deceased,

33
00:02:18,980 --> 00:02:20,620
and he’s inciting Empress Dowager
to imitate Wu Zetian,

34
00:02:20,900 --> 00:02:21,860
flattering her.

35
00:02:22,260 --> 00:02:22,980
Isn’t this what

36
00:02:22,980 --> 00:02:24,420
crafty sycophant would do?

37
00:02:25,980 --> 00:02:27,140
We can’t judge someone or something

38
00:02:27,820 --> 00:02:29,700
without the context.

39
00:02:33,380 --> 00:02:34,780
Then what’s the context of

40
00:02:34,900 --> 00:02:36,180
Cheng offering the painting?

41
00:02:37,500 --> 00:02:40,580
What he did is not appropriate,

42
00:02:41,060 --> 00:02:43,100
but we can’t tell if he meant well or not.

43
00:02:43,900 --> 00:02:46,660
Back then, there were many treacherous
officials like Ding Wei

44
00:02:47,100 --> 00:02:48,700
who attempted to disrupt the court

45
00:02:49,380 --> 00:02:51,100
when you were still young and
the country was unsettled.

46
00:02:51,980 --> 00:02:55,580
Cheng Lin is not the only one

47
00:02:55,580 --> 00:02:56,700
who wishes the Empress Dowager

48
00:02:57,020 --> 00:02:58,060
to take the power

49
00:02:58,060 --> 00:02:59,540
to protect the court

50
00:03:00,020 --> 00:03:01,380
from the treacherous.

51
00:03:02,460 --> 00:03:04,380
They might not be crafty sycophants.

52
00:03:05,500 --> 00:03:07,460
But by comparing Empress Dowager
as the Empress Dowager Wu,

53
00:03:07,980 --> 00:03:09,980
wasn’t he comparing me to Li Xian

54
00:03:10,460 --> 00:03:11,580
who’s been a puppet

55
00:03:11,580 --> 00:03:12,980
controlled by a woman his whole life?

56
00:03:14,060 --> 00:03:16,940
Empress Dowager Wu took the throne

57
00:03:17,580 --> 00:03:18,940
because

58
00:03:19,020 --> 00:03:21,620
her young sons couldn’t control the court

59
00:03:22,580 --> 00:03:23,860
the Emperor was young and
the country was unsettled,

60
00:03:23,980 --> 00:03:26,620
which made all vassals feel insecure.

61
00:03:26,980 --> 00:03:27,820
But,

62
00:03:28,660 --> 00:03:31,540
an Emperor won’t stay young forever.

63
00:03:32,580 --> 00:03:35,180
Whether he becomes a puppet or not

64
00:03:35,300 --> 00:03:37,220
does not depend on what an official says,

65
00:03:37,340 --> 00:03:39,580
or Empress Dowager behind the curtain,

66
00:03:40,060 --> 00:03:42,860
but on you, Your Majesty.

67
00:03:47,300 --> 00:03:48,580
Then what do you think

68
00:03:50,100 --> 00:03:51,780
is the most important thing

69
00:03:52,580 --> 00:03:53,700
to become the Emperor that everybody wants?

70
00:03:58,220 --> 00:03:58,900
Your Majesty,

71
00:03:59,420 --> 00:04:02,180
I’m going to teach you The Book of Documents.

72
00:04:02,180 --> 00:04:03,700
= The Book of Documents =

73
00:04:07,700 --> 00:04:09,620
Gao Tao is talking with Da Yu
about being an Emperor.

74
00:04:10,020 --> 00:04:12,060
He believes the Emperor is the leading
example of all people,

75
00:04:12,860 --> 00:04:14,380
but he put being discreet

76
00:04:14,460 --> 00:04:16,460
prior to many other good virtues.

77
00:04:17,260 --> 00:04:20,140
Later, they talk about the nine
virtues of an Emperor,

78
00:04:20,620 --> 00:04:22,500
and once again put benevolence and
discreetness on the top of the list.

79
00:04:30,740 --> 00:04:32,140
By teaching me the strategies of Gao Tao
in The Book of Documents,

80
00:04:32,500 --> 00:04:34,060
are you trying to tell me

81
00:04:34,500 --> 00:04:35,500
ruling the country

82
00:04:35,500 --> 00:04:36,900
is not about expanding your territory,

83
00:04:36,900 --> 00:04:37,900
and achieving success,

84
00:04:38,020 --> 00:04:39,820
but acting with caution and forbearance.

85
00:04:40,260 --> 00:04:41,940
Why don’t you just change it into Endurance?

86
00:04:58,980 --> 00:04:59,860
I was forgetting my manners,

87
00:05:00,180 --> 00:05:01,220
forgive me.

88
00:05:04,100 --> 00:05:05,820
May I write something?

89
00:05:16,620 --> 00:05:19,500
= Benevolence =

90
00:05:23,260 --> 00:05:26,100
The prudence of an Emperor comes from benevolence.

91
00:05:26,780 --> 00:05:28,980
The prudence of an Emperor is to keep
from making mistakes.

92
00:05:29,500 --> 00:05:30,700
He worries

93
00:05:31,100 --> 00:05:32,460
just because he knows

94
00:05:33,100 --> 00:05:34,180
how powerful he is.

95
00:05:35,300 --> 00:05:36,020
Powerful?

96
00:05:37,100 --> 00:05:38,140
Because of his power?

97
00:05:39,700 --> 00:05:41,860
The Emperor holds the utmost power,

98
00:05:42,300 --> 00:05:44,020
anything he says can either be a blessing

99
00:05:44,220 --> 00:05:46,780
or a curse to all the people.

100
00:05:48,180 --> 00:05:49,740
If an emperor can’t be benevolent,

101
00:05:49,980 --> 00:05:52,020
can’t understand and feel what people suffer from,

102
00:05:52,420 --> 00:05:55,620
he can of course be arbitrary and willful,

103
00:05:55,740 --> 00:05:56,700
and has no worries

104
00:05:57,660 --> 00:06:00,940
or endure anything.

105
00:06:13,780 --> 00:06:14,580
= Nanjing Academy =
This is the hottest summer

106
00:06:14,580 --> 00:06:15,740
in a dozen of years.

107
00:06:16,580 --> 00:06:17,700
You can directly fry eggs

108
00:06:17,860 --> 00:06:19,060
on the ground.

109
00:06:19,860 --> 00:06:20,780
There’s not a single drop of rain

110
00:06:21,260 --> 00:06:22,380
for two months.

111
00:06:22,380 --> 00:06:23,100
= Cao Danshu =

112
00:06:23,100 --> 00:06:24,260
= Cao Danshu =
The weather is weird.

113
00:06:24,780 --> 00:06:26,540
Some people nearby died from the heat.

114
00:06:27,420 --> 00:06:28,260
I heard

115
00:06:28,260 --> 00:06:30,020
His Majesty has reduced to one meal a day

116
00:06:30,660 --> 00:06:32,500
and went to Kaibao Temple to pray for rain.

117
00:06:33,500 --> 00:06:35,140
If the Heaven is irritated

118
00:06:35,140 --> 00:06:36,140
by something,

119
00:06:36,980 --> 00:06:38,460
please give us some rain

120
00:06:38,580 --> 00:06:39,860
for the sake of His Majesty.

121
00:06:43,860 --> 00:06:44,980
Cutting his meal

122
00:06:45,460 --> 00:06:47,180
is just a posturing to us.

123
00:06:48,020 --> 00:06:49,220
How can it bring rain?

124
00:06:50,300 --> 00:06:53,140
= Fan Zhongyan, courtesy name Xiwen =
His Majesty blames himself for drought,

125
00:06:53,820 --> 00:06:55,620
just to posture

126
00:06:55,700 --> 00:06:56,980
to the people?

127
00:06:57,300 --> 00:06:58,100
Mr. Fan.

128
00:06:58,380 --> 00:06:59,220
Mr. Fan.

129
00:07:11,620 --> 00:07:12,380
Tongshu.

130
00:07:23,700 --> 00:07:24,540
Magistrate Yan.

131
00:07:25,100 --> 00:07:25,780
Mr. Fan.

132
00:07:26,780 --> 00:07:27,900
I’ve been looking forward to seeing you, Mr. Fan.

133
00:07:28,900 --> 00:07:31,180
This is the principle graduate in the
fifth year of Tiansheng,

134
00:07:31,180 --> 00:07:32,140
Wang Yaochen.

135
00:07:32,380 --> 00:07:35,100
He’s the official in charge of compiling national
history in the Secretariat in the capital,

136
00:07:35,100 --> 00:07:35,980
and an official of
the Academy of Talents and Knowledge.

137
00:07:36,500 --> 00:07:38,300
His Majesty sent him to Nanjing

138
00:07:38,900 --> 00:07:40,260
for the drought in Nanjing and the Capital

139
00:07:40,380 --> 00:07:41,500
to bring some prescriptions

140
00:07:41,500 --> 00:07:42,940
organized and reviewed

141
00:07:42,940 --> 00:07:44,820
by the Imperial Academy,

142
00:07:45,100 --> 00:07:48,260
which can help Nanjing officials fight against
the drought and prevent epidemic

143
00:07:48,260 --> 00:07:49,140
by giving out medicines.

144
00:07:49,380 --> 00:07:50,660
He’s also appointed by His Majesty

145
00:07:50,820 --> 00:07:53,180
to investigate the condition of the disaster
in Nanjing and what people need here

146
00:07:53,500 --> 00:07:55,460
so that the court can relieve the people.

147
00:07:57,260 --> 00:07:58,420
Thank you, Mr. Wang.

148
00:07:59,860 --> 00:08:01,340
I’d like to ask Mr. Fan

149
00:08:01,580 --> 00:08:02,820
to choose some students in the academy

150
00:08:03,060 --> 00:08:04,100
to copy some prescriptions

151
00:08:04,300 --> 00:08:05,180
and make medicines accordingly.

152
00:08:05,940 --> 00:08:07,100
I’ll choose

153
00:08:07,300 --> 00:08:08,900
about ten prudent students right now.

154
00:08:13,380 --> 00:08:14,700
Seeing the Emperor

155
00:08:14,700 --> 00:08:16,220
has the demeanor of a benevolent emperor

156
00:08:16,380 --> 00:08:18,140
who can handle the situation well,

157
00:08:18,580 --> 00:08:19,820
I’ve proposed last month

158
00:08:19,860 --> 00:08:22,180
that the Emperor is a grown-up now,

159
00:08:22,780 --> 00:08:24,860
should take the court.

160
00:08:25,980 --> 00:08:27,300
But my words are of little effect.

161
00:08:27,900 --> 00:08:30,100
If Magistrate Yan

162
00:08:30,380 --> 00:08:31,740
can write a joint proposal

163
00:08:31,740 --> 00:08:33,220
with other major officials,

164
00:08:33,420 --> 00:08:34,700
it will definitely make a difference.

165
00:08:35,220 --> 00:08:36,620
- Mr. Fan. - I understand

166
00:08:37,700 --> 00:08:38,660
what you just taught me.

167
00:08:40,060 --> 00:08:41,020
His Majesty is afraid of the Heaven,

168
00:08:41,340 --> 00:08:43,420
so he blamed himself by
cutting his meal for drought

169
00:08:43,740 --> 00:08:45,180
to review the policies

170
00:08:45,260 --> 00:08:46,220
he made before.

171
00:08:46,900 --> 00:08:48,100
Then he devoted manpower

172
00:08:48,180 --> 00:08:49,300
into relieving the disaster.

173
00:08:49,780 --> 00:08:50,860
His respect to Heaven

174
00:08:50,860 --> 00:08:53,220
is based on his love to the people.

175
00:08:55,380 --> 00:08:57,020
What you read

176
00:08:57,020 --> 00:08:57,980
and learnt here, Cao,

177
00:08:58,340 --> 00:09:00,380
might not be directly contributive to the court,

178
00:09:00,580 --> 00:09:01,660
but can still cultivate your moral character,

179
00:09:01,700 --> 00:09:04,260
which will be of great help

180
00:09:04,660 --> 00:09:05,940
in the future.

181
00:09:08,140 --> 00:09:09,780
My future husband wants nothing but being immortal.

182
00:09:10,220 --> 00:09:11,100
He doesn’t need me.

183
00:09:13,260 --> 00:09:13,940
Sir,

184
00:09:16,940 --> 00:09:17,940
can I help

185
00:09:18,260 --> 00:09:20,100
investigate and record

186
00:09:20,100 --> 00:09:21,140
the disaster?

187
00:09:22,180 --> 00:09:23,820
So that I can do something for
His Majesty and the people

188
00:09:23,860 --> 00:09:26,020
as a student in the academy.

189
00:09:27,500 --> 00:09:29,580
You attended the academy

190
00:09:29,580 --> 00:09:30,820
in your brother’s name.

191
00:09:30,860 --> 00:09:31,940
This might be improper.

192
00:09:31,940 --> 00:09:32,780
I think

193
00:09:33,940 --> 00:09:34,980
you should…

194
00:09:34,980 --> 00:09:35,900
In Confucian classics, history,
philosophy and literature,

195
00:09:36,540 --> 00:09:38,300
am I not better than others

196
00:09:39,060 --> 00:09:40,300
that disappointed you,

197
00:09:41,460 --> 00:09:43,180
or I caused any troubles and broke any rules?

198
00:09:44,100 --> 00:09:45,420
If I did anything wrong,

199
00:09:45,980 --> 00:09:46,820
please tell me

200
00:09:47,180 --> 00:09:48,700
and I shall correct it.

201
00:09:49,380 --> 00:09:50,300
You did nothing wrong.

202
00:09:51,260 --> 00:09:52,660
The Loyalty to the emperor

203
00:09:52,660 --> 00:09:54,140
you learnt here

204
00:09:55,180 --> 00:09:56,100
is excellent.

205
00:10:18,340 --> 00:10:19,860
Zhigui, thank you for your hard work.

206
00:10:20,220 --> 00:10:21,260
Thanks to you

207
00:10:21,540 --> 00:10:23,300
for investigating people’s life these years

208
00:10:23,660 --> 00:10:25,500
so that you are familiar with

209
00:10:25,940 --> 00:10:27,860
those shop owners and common people,

210
00:10:28,740 --> 00:10:30,980
the disaster investigation,

211
00:10:30,980 --> 00:10:32,100
medicine distribution

212
00:10:32,620 --> 00:10:33,740
and statistics collection

213
00:10:34,020 --> 00:10:35,940
can be done so quickly and smoothly.

214
00:10:37,340 --> 00:10:38,740
= Han Qi, courtesy name Zhigui =
You can reduce

215
00:10:39,060 --> 00:10:42,820
people’s misunderstandings and suspicions.

216
00:10:44,020 --> 00:10:45,300
You flattered me, Your Majesty.

217
00:10:46,100 --> 00:10:47,380
This time, my colleagues

218
00:10:47,620 --> 00:10:49,980
feel deeply about your benevolence to people

219
00:10:50,300 --> 00:10:51,700
and the opportunity you gave us.

220
00:10:52,180 --> 00:10:53,380
They all fully devote themselves
into this endeavor.

221
00:10:54,220 --> 00:10:56,500
I can’t take all the credit.

222
00:10:58,660 --> 00:10:59,460
Excellent.

223
00:11:00,260 --> 00:11:02,860
You’ve learnt to be modest these years.

224
00:11:05,700 --> 00:11:08,300
I was arrogant when I was young.

225
00:11:08,780 --> 00:11:09,700
I’d rather not to think about it.

226
00:11:16,180 --> 00:11:18,540
Your Majesty, there’s another thing.

227
00:11:21,060 --> 00:11:21,700
What is it?

228
00:11:22,940 --> 00:11:25,220
I heard the Cabinet has hold a few proposals

229
00:11:25,700 --> 00:11:26,700
from Fan Zhongyan,

230
00:11:26,740 --> 00:11:28,300
Teng Zongliang and some other people

231
00:11:29,420 --> 00:11:32,900
who asked the Empress Dowager to
step down and give the office to you.

232
00:11:40,580 --> 00:11:42,060
I heard Empress Dowager feel sick

233
00:11:42,260 --> 00:11:43,740
so I’ll go back early

234
00:11:44,060 --> 00:11:46,220
to visit her and serve her medicine.

235
00:11:47,460 --> 00:11:48,140
Yes, Your Majesty.

236
00:12:02,820 --> 00:12:04,220
Redress my hair

237
00:12:04,540 --> 00:12:06,300
and clean my face with the napkin.

238
00:12:07,020 --> 00:12:07,900
Once we are back

239
00:12:07,900 --> 00:12:09,140
we’ll skip the dress changing

240
00:12:09,140 --> 00:12:10,220
and go to see Empress Dowager directly.

241
00:12:10,220 --> 00:12:11,220
Yes, Your Majesty.

242
00:12:21,780 --> 00:12:22,820
He has grown up.

243
00:12:25,700 --> 00:12:27,420
He has grown up so soon.

244
00:12:29,780 --> 00:12:30,820
So soon.

245
00:12:32,100 --> 00:12:32,940
Your Majesty,

246
00:12:33,220 --> 00:12:34,700
Officer Ren told me to report

247
00:12:34,780 --> 00:12:36,180
His Majesty will come to visit you

248
00:12:36,380 --> 00:12:37,740
directly from Kaibao Temple.

249
00:12:43,660 --> 00:12:46,500
Tell Juan to dress my hair.

250
00:12:49,780 --> 00:12:50,540
Xinhe,

251
00:12:51,420 --> 00:12:53,820
give me the powder and rouge.

252
00:12:59,100 --> 00:13:01,860
Is there a smell in the hall?

253
00:13:04,060 --> 00:13:04,940
Burn some incense.

254
00:13:09,940 --> 00:13:11,420
I had some medicine yesterday,

255
00:13:11,780 --> 00:13:13,180
and feel much better today.

256
00:13:14,140 --> 00:13:15,860
You’ve been having tough days.

257
00:13:16,700 --> 00:13:18,100
You’ve been reducing your meals,

258
00:13:18,500 --> 00:13:21,500
blaming and reviewing yourself in the temple.

259
00:13:23,100 --> 00:13:25,980
You even assigned royal doctors
to inquire patients.

260
00:13:26,620 --> 00:13:27,900
You set up mat shelter at major intersections

261
00:13:28,500 --> 00:13:30,500
to give out tea and medicines.

262
00:13:32,220 --> 00:13:33,900
I didn’t think of this

263
00:13:34,740 --> 00:13:36,220
until I had heatstroke.

264
00:13:38,020 --> 00:13:39,540
When I told Lv Yijian to do that,

265
00:13:39,540 --> 00:13:41,860
I found you’ve done it already.

266
00:13:42,980 --> 00:13:44,140
You’ve been showing the talent and heart of

267
00:13:44,140 --> 00:13:46,060
a wise emperor these days.

268
00:13:47,380 --> 00:13:49,060
And you can keep calm and low

269
00:13:50,340 --> 00:13:51,940
to settle everything down.

270
00:13:53,060 --> 00:13:54,060
You didn’t even mention anything

271
00:13:54,500 --> 00:13:55,860
to me.

272
00:13:58,700 --> 00:13:59,500
Excellent work.

273
00:13:59,500 --> 00:14:00,860
Someone else should take the credit

274
00:14:01,780 --> 00:14:03,420
to your praise.

275
00:14:05,140 --> 00:14:06,820
I really don’t want to

276
00:14:07,020 --> 00:14:07,820
give the honor back to him

277
00:14:08,540 --> 00:14:10,260
but I can’t deceive

278
