00:29:45,100 --> 00:29:45,940
to sell.

559
00:29:46,020 --> 00:29:47,820
You have to buy
at the price fixed by the government.

560
00:29:48,100 --> 00:29:49,460
You don’t have a choice

561
00:29:49,620 --> 00:29:50,540
