612
00:33:33,500 --> 00:33:35,220
Your Majesty.

613
00:33:39,940 --> 00:33:41,820
Your Majesty.

614
00:33:42,340 --> 00:33:44,900
According to the law,

615
00:33:44,900 --> 00:33:47,460
